data.description: Location, Location, Location….. Excellent opportunity to purchase an "as-is" home is across from Gesu Church and school and near John Carroll, shopping and schools. There is a half bath on the first floor. Primary bathroom has been newly remodeled with a beautiful walk-in tiled shower, fireplace in the bedroom and a large walk-in closet measuring 14 x 8 with an additional closet inside. A full bath on the second floor and a full bath on the third floor with a bedroom. There is a morning room adjacent to the dining room. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances and concrete countertops. Hardwood flooring throughout the home. The living room is large with a fireplace and beautiful floor to ceiling windows that bring a lot of light into the living room. There is a 2-car detached garage. Buyer to assume University Heights Point of Sale (POS) inspection.
